fields.summary: ActiveMQ 5.4.2 Admin - Accessing Scheduled.jsp giving an Exception in log file

comments.body: workaround: scheduler support needs to be enabled for the broker. <broker schedulerSupport="true" ../>
This is duplicate of https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3088, which is resolved on the trunk
